category: Devel
requires: mingw64-i686-bzip2 mingw64-i686-gcc-core mingw64-i686-libpng mingw64-i686-zlib pkg-config
sdesc: "TrueType font engine for Win32 toolchain"
ldesc: "FreeType is a freely available software library
 to render fonts. It is written in C, designed to be small,
 efficient, highly customizable, and portable while capable
 of producing high-quality output (glyph images) of most
 vector and bitmap font formats."

